body:
It should have been fetched automatically. 
Try

```
unzip /tmp/inception5h.zip -d tensorflow/examples/android/assets/
```

Then rebuild, the apk, `unzip -v` to make sure it's there. Then `adb install -r` to re-install on your phone.
